SecurityRAG

AI-powered Security Knowledge Assistant using Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG).

Overview

SecurityRAG enables security analysts to ask natural language questions and receive contextual answers from trusted cybersecurity knowledge sources.

The platform retrieves relevant information from:

MITRE ATT&CK
Sigma Rules
Security Playbooks
Microsoft Security Documentation
Threat Intelligence Sources
DFIR Knowledge Base
Features
Natural language security queries
Vector-based semantic search
MITRE ATT&CK mapping
Source citations
Threat investigation assistance
Incident response guidance
Security documentation retrieval
Example Questions
Explain T1059.
What does Event ID 4625 mean?
Investigate suspicious PowerShell activity.
Show Sigma rules for credential dumping.
Recommend containment steps for ransomware.
